  "notes": [
    "This study represents the first comprehensive genomic analysis of chimpanzee hepatocellular carcinoma compared to human HCC",
    "The high frequency of TSC2 mutations in chimpanzee HCC (80%) versus human HCC (7%) suggests species-specific oncogenic pathways",
